3. £1.49 - MAX98357 Audio Chip            https://www.digikey.co.uk/en/products/detail/analog-devices-inc-maxim-integrated/MAX98357AETE-T/4936122
4. £0.30 - Micro Speaker                  https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/Best-Selling-8ohm-1-0W-900HZ_1601224274783.html
5. £0.26 - RGB LED                        https://www.digikey.co.uk/en/products/detail/cree-led/CLY6D-FKC-CK1N1D1BB7D3D3/5321303
6. £4.00 - Custom PSU & 18650 (Estimated)
7. £0.08 - Micro Switch SS-5GL            https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/New-Original-OMROM-SS-5GL-3PIN_1601789370776.html
8. £1.00 - PCB and PCBA (Estimated)

(6. Custom PSU estimate is based on 50% of the price of a single off-the-shelf PSU)
(8. Most PCB Assembly includes free Resistors and Capacitors)

Considerable further savings may be available by buying directly from suppliers in China, rather than DigiKey, e.g. ESP32-WROVER-E-N8R8 Module is quoted at £0.38 on AliBaba.

Estimated Total Cost, all parts (except enclosure), based on > 2500 Quantity, using DigiKey for all critical parts (except printer) = £17.50
